---
title: Souvlaki Style Lamb Koftas on Flatbread with Paprika Wedges, Pomegranate Seeds and Mint Yoghurt
description: We love good Souvlaki Style Lamb Koftas and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/souvlaki-style-lamb-koftas-b3ce4cc1-6058eee5.jpg
